Generate crop boxes of varying sizes for multiscale image processing, with layered overlapping regions.

**Args**

Name| Type| Description| Default  
---|---|---|---  
`im_size`| `tuple[int, ...]`| Height and width of the input image.| _required_  
`n_layers`| `int`| Number of layers to generate crop boxes for.| _required_  
